Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Allies didn't bother defending where the Germans actually came through. Well, Sutherland\Nand I could have told them in a second, couldn't we, Sutherland? We could have told them in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a second.\NSo you see, the significance of being able to know the differences between truth and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,falsehood, plus you can tell at any time, any place about anything, is really critical.\NIt's not necessarily quite mind-boggling. In a way, it really is a fulcrum, on which
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the history of mankind can actually make a change. Well, the history of mankind did make\Na change in very recent times. Using kinesiology, you can find out for yourself. Everything
